ive/public/2022-11/dont-look-now-1973-donald-sutherland.jpg/960x540-cropped/dont-look-now-1973-donald-sutherland.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"/><p class="PreviewCard__description">Set in off-season Venice, British director Nicolas Roeg’s tragedy combines an acute study of grief with a supernaturally charged thriller plot, to beautiful and devastating effect.</p></div><span id="rank-114" class="ResultsPage__Span-sc-of10co-3 kvXPxe"></span><p class="ResultsPage__P-sc-of10co-2 eUEyPc">1973<!-- --> <!-- -->United Kingdom, Italy</p><p class="ResultsPage__P-sc-of10co-2 eUEyPc">Directed by <!-- -->Nicolas Roeg</p></a></article><article id="b8c13f8d-489f-55c1-beb5-315c9b12f517" class="PreviewCard__Article-sc-7y1ad6-0 gUNVnM"><a href="/film/b8c13f8d-489f-55c1-beb5-315c9b12f517/nashville"><h1>Nashville</h1><div class="PreviewCard__image"><p class="ResultsPage__Rank-sc-of10co-1 gsVRkZ PreviewCard__label">=<!-- -->114</p><img src="https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/responsive/public/2022-12/nashville-1975-henry-gibson-arms-outstretched-on-stage-microphone.jpg/960x540-cropped/nashville-1975-henry-gibson-arms-outstretched-on-stage-microphone.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"/><p class="PreviewCard__description">Made to celebrate the bicentennial of American Independence, Robert Altman’s footloose epic blends the lives of 24 characters in the capital of country music.</p></div><span id="rank-114" class="ResultsPage__Span-sc-of10co-3 kvXPxe"></span><p class="ResultsPage__P-sc-of10co-2 eUEyPc">1975<!-- --> <!-- -->USA</p><p class="ResultsPage__P-sc-of10co-2 eUEyPc">Directed by <!-- -->Robert Altman</p></a></article><article id="59ac010c-250e-5a0e-8cdf-65c3c5217634" class="PreviewCard__Article-sc-7y1ad6-0 gUNVnM"><a href="/film/59ac010c-250e-5a0e-8cdf-65c3c5217634/a-woman-under-the-influence"><h1>A Woman under the Influence</h1><div class="PreviewCard__image"><p class="ResultsPage__Rank-sc-of10co-1 gsVRkZ PreviewCard__label">=<!-- -->114</p><img src="https://core-cms.bfi.or