85-8885-8a5ed081f99e/the-leopard"><h1>The Leopard</h1><div class="PreviewCard__image"><p class="ResultsPage__Rank-sc-of10co-1 gsVRkZ PreviewCard__label">=<!-- -->90</p><img src="https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/responsive/public/2021-07/the-leopard-1963-burt-lancaster-claudia-cardinale-ballroom.jpeg/960x540-cropped/the-leopard-1963-burt-lancaster-claudia-cardinale-ballroom.jpeg" alt="" loading="lazy"/><p class="PreviewCard__description">Luchino Visconti’s sumptuous epic portrays the fall of 19th-century Sicilian nobility, its decadent displays of wealth tinged with melancholy.</p></div><span id="rank-90" class="ResultsPage__Span-sc-of10co-3 kvXPxe"></span><p class="ResultsPage__P-sc-of10co-2 eUEyPc">1963<!-- --> <!-- -->Italy, France</p><p class="ResultsPage__P-sc-of10co-2 eUEyPc">Directed by <!-- -->Luchino Visconti</p></a></article><article id="9d40327d-d060-56c2-86bb-36d8a6c18561" class="PreviewCard__Article-sc-7y1ad6-0 gUNVnM"><a href="/film/9d40327d-d060-56c2-86bb-36d8a6c18561/madame-de"><h1>Madame de...</h1><div class="PreviewCard__image"><p class="ResultsPage__Rank-sc-of10co-1 gsVRkZ PreviewCard__label">=<!-- -->90</p><img src="https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/responsive/public/2022-11/madame-de-1953-small-mirror-reflection.jpg/960x540-cropped/madame-de-1953-small-mirror-reflection.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"/><p class="PreviewCard__description">Max Ophuls’ woozy whirligig tracks a pair of unwanted earrings around high-society Paris – until they bear the weight of lost time and passion.</p></div><span id="rank-90" class="ResultsPage__Span-sc-of10co-3 kvXPxe"></span><p class="ResultsPage__P-sc-of10co-2 eUEyPc">1953<!-- --> <!-- -->France, Italy</p><p class="ResultsPage__P-sc-of10co-2 eUEyPc">Directed by <!-- -->Max Ophuls</p></a></article><article id="4d39487e-a464-5771-a2f3-2533c7ba9c8c" class="PreviewCard__Article-sc-7y1ad6-0 gUNVnM"><a href="/film/4d39487e-a464-5771-a2f3-2533c7ba9c8c/the-shining"><h1>The Shining</h