<!-- -->78</p><img src="https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/responsive/public/2020-09/sunset-boulevard-1950-gloria-swanson-holding-hand-to-projector-light.jpg/960x540-cropped/sunset-boulevard-1950-gloria-swanson-holding-hand-to-projector-light.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"/><p class="PreviewCard__description">Tinseltown’s greatest self-satire, a gothic requiem for big-screen bygones and the highs of screen stardom.</p></div><span id="rank-78" class="ResultsPage__Span-sc-of10co-3 kvXPxe"></span><p class="ResultsPage__P-sc-of10co-2 eUEyPc">1950<!-- --> <!-- -->USA</p><p class="ResultsPage__P-sc-of10co-2 eUEyPc">Directed by <!-- -->Billy Wilder</p></a></article><article id="b33aea00-58f0-58ce-99b8-2fe7800be94d" class="PreviewCard__Article-sc-7y1ad6-0 gUNVnM"><a href="/film/b33aea00-58f0-58ce-99b8-2fe7800be94d/celine-and-julie-go-boating"><h1>Céline and Julie Go Boating</h1><div class="PreviewCard__image"><p class="ResultsPage__Rank-sc-of10co-1 gsVRkZ PreviewCard__label">=<!-- -->78</p><img src="https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/responsive/public/2022-11/celine-and-julie-go-boating-1974-cards-on-head.jpg/960x540-cropped/celine-and-julie-go-boating-1974-cards-on-head.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"/><p class="PreviewCard__description">Jacques Rivette’s most playful, innovative frolic, in which his irreverent Parisian heroines dissolve worlds, genres, social codes and boundaries.</p></div><span id="rank-78" class="ResultsPage__Span-sc-of10co-3 kvXPxe"></span><p class="ResultsPage__P-sc-of10co-2 eUEyPc">1974<!-- --> <!-- -->France</p><p class="ResultsPage__P-sc-of10co-2 eUEyPc">Directed by <!-- -->Jacques Rivette</p></a></article><article id="0e535956-629b-5e96-8fdc-6c6034fef935" class="PreviewCard__Article-sc-7y1ad6-0 gUNVnM"><a href="/film/0e535956-629b-5e96-8fdc-6c6034fef935/a-brighter-summer-day"><h1>A Brighter Summer Day</h1><div class="PreviewCard__image"><p class="ResultsPage__Rank-sc-of10co-1 gsVRkZ PreviewCard__label">=<!-- -->78</p