6-bfb3-200802199b37/ordet"><h1>Ordet</h1><div class="PreviewCard__image"><p class="ResultsPage__Rank-sc-of10co-1 gsVRkZ PreviewCard__label">=<!-- -->48</p><img src="https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/responsive/public/2022-01/ordet-1955-funeral-high-angle.jpg/960x540-cropped/ordet-1955-funeral-high-angle.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"/><p class="PreviewCard__description">An austere parable on the power of faith, Carl Theodor Dreyer’s penultimate film culminates in a transcendent resurrection scene.</p></div><span id="rank-48" class="ResultsPage__Span-sc-of10co-3 kvXPxe"></span><p class="ResultsPage__P-sc-of10co-2 eUEyPc">1955<!-- --> <!-- -->Denmark</p><p class="ResultsPage__P-sc-of10co-2 eUEyPc">Directed by <!-- -->Carl Th. Dreyer</p></a></article><article id="82acb1a1-c6c7-5478-a27e-b0c76e0d244c" class="PreviewCard__Article-sc-7y1ad6-0 gUNVnM"><a href="/film/82acb1a1-c6c7-5478-a27e-b0c76e0d244c/wanda"><h1>Wanda</h1><div class="PreviewCard__image"><p class="ResultsPage__Rank-sc-of10co-1 gsVRkZ PreviewCard__label">=<!-- -->48</p><img src="https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/responsive/public/2022-11/wanda-1970-barbara-loden-at-door.jpeg/960x540-cropped/wanda-1970-barbara-loden-at-door.jpeg" alt="" loading="lazy"/><p class="PreviewCard__description">Barbara Loden’s tough, unsentimental portrait of a woman adrift in the industrial heartlands of the north-eastern United States.</p></div><span id="rank-48" class="ResultsPage__Span-sc-of10co-3 kvXPxe"></span><p class="ResultsPage__P-sc-of10co-2 eUEyPc">1970<!-- --> <!-- -->USA</p><p class="ResultsPage__P-sc-of10co-2 eUEyPc">Directed by <!-- -->Barbara Loden</p></a></article><article id="7232754d-299f-5b3c-9c4e-f1758809c8ed" class="PreviewCard__Article-sc-7y1ad6-0 gUNVnM"><a href="/film/7232754d-299f-5b3c-9c4e-f1758809c8ed/barry-lyndon"><h1>Barry Lyndon</h1><div class="PreviewCard__image"><p class="ResultsPage__Rank-sc-of10co-1 gsVRkZ PreviewCard__label">=<!-- -->45</p><img src="https://