86ef-2887a36a393a" class="PreviewCard__Article-sc-7y1ad6-0 gUNVnM"><a href="/film/313424b8-8d3b-5180-86ef-2887a36a393a/the-night-of-the-hunter"><h1>The Night of the Hunter</h1><div class="PreviewCard__image"><p class="ResultsPage__Rank-sc-of10co-1 gsVRkZ PreviewCard__label">=<!-- -->25</p><img src="https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/responsive/public/2022-02/the-night-of-the-hunter-1955-robert-mitchum-love-tattoo.jpg/960x540-cropped/the-night-of-the-hunter-1955-robert-mitchum-love-tattoo.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"/><p class="PreviewCard__description">Actor Charles Laughton’s only film as director, starring Robert Mitchum as an implacable child-hunting preacher, still leaves an indelible mark.</p></div><span id="rank-25" class="ResultsPage__Span-sc-of10co-3 kvXPxe"></span><p class="ResultsPage__P-sc-of10co-2 eUEyPc">1955<!-- --> <!-- -->USA</p><p class="ResultsPage__P-sc-of10co-2 eUEyPc">Directed by <!-- -->Charles Laughton</p></a></article><article id="3fc31e95-d0aa-5a28-a8d4-4d3c8a3d50a9" class="PreviewCard__Article-sc-7y1ad6-0 gUNVnM"><a href="/film/3fc31e95-d0aa-5a28-a8d4-4d3c8a3d50a9/au-hasard-balthazar"><h1>Au hasard Balthazar</h1><div class="PreviewCard__image"><p class="ResultsPage__Rank-sc-of10co-1 gsVRkZ PreviewCard__label">=<!-- -->25</p><img src="https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/responsive/public/2022-03/au-hasard-balthazar-1966-girl-donkey.jpg/960x540-cropped/au-hasard-balthazar-1966-girl-donkey.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"/><p class="PreviewCard__description">Robert Bresson gave us a typically stark vision of humanity as experienced by a put-upon, maltreated beast of burden that passes from owner to owner.</p></div><span id="rank-25" class="ResultsPage__Span-sc-of10co-3 kvXPxe"></span><p class="ResultsPage__P-sc-of10co-2 eUEyPc">1966<!-- --> <!-- -->France, Sweden</p><p class="ResultsPage__P-sc-of10co-2 eUEyPc">Directed by <!-- -->Robert Bresson</p></a></article><article id="8e81a2c0-b1e4-51c4-b5da-93458d361dc3" c