 but to their own ludicrous delusions of recreating European society in an indifferent, wholly alien landscape. Most extreme in this madness is Don Lope de Aguirre (Klaus Kinski), whose megalomaniac scheming proceeds from the mutinous to the murderous. At once a stirring but avowedly unsentimental tale of overweening ambition and a remarkably rich and original variation on the adventure film, Herzog’s masterpiece combines a flair for the epic with moments of incisive miniaturist observation. The images are breathtaking in their beauty, mystery and sense of scale; Kinski’s performance was arguably his best ever; and the sharp insights into human folly – sometimes sorrowful, sometimes darkly witty – typify Herzog at his most caustically effective.</p>\r\n","quote":null,"credits":{"director":"Werner Herzog","producer":"Werner Herzog","writer":"Werner Herzog","featuring":"Klaus Kinski, Cecilia Rivera, Ruy Guerra"},"year":"1972","nameAndYear":"Aguirre, Wrath of God (1972)","links":{"player":"https://player.bfi.org.uk/subscription/film/watch-aguirre-wrath-of-god-1972-online","southbank":""},"player":{"url":"https://player.bfi.org.uk/subscription/film/watch-aguirre-wrath-of-god-1972-online","cta":"https://player.bfi.org.uk/subscribe/5598","pillar":"subscription","price":0,"duration":0},"performances":[],"tags":["BFI Player"],"productionCountries":"Federal Republic of Germany","runningTime":95,"sightAndSound":null,"products":[]}},{"rank":114,"tied":true,"film":{"uuid":"8c6c178c-b903-5e2b-b480-d43a6b21f5b4","image":{"base":"https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/","relative":"2022-11/dont-look-now-1973-donald-sutherland.jpg","main":"https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/responsive/public/2022-11/dont-look-now-1973-donald-sutherland.jpg/1920x1080-cropped/dont-look-now-1973-donald-sutherland.jpg","thumb":"https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/responsive/public/2022-11/dont-look-now-1973-donald-sutherland.jpg/960x540-cropped/dont-look-