ly in the Tennessee state capital.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A radical reimagining of the movie musical, this satire on the Nashville scene features a host of original songs, many of which were written by members of the ensemble cast.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In 2006, Altman turned his attentions to another great musical city, recalling the 1930s jazz culture of his youth in Kansas City.</p>\r\n","quote":null,"credits":{"director":"Robert Altman","producer":"Robert Altman","writer":"Joan Tewkesbury","featuring":"David Arkin, Barbara Baxley, Ned Beatty"},"year":"1975","nameAndYear":"Nashville (1975)","links":{"player":"","southbank":""},"player":null,"performances":[],"tags":[],"productionCountries":"USA","runningTime":0,"sightAndSound":null,"products":[]}},{"rank":114,"tied":true,"film":{"uuid":"59ac010c-250e-5a0e-8cdf-65c3c5217634","image":{"base":"https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/","relative":"2022-02/a-woman-under-the-influence-1974-gena-rowlands-dinner-table.jpg","main":"https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/responsive/public/2022-02/a-woman-under-the-influence-1974-gena-rowlands-dinner-table.jpg/1920x1080-cropped/a-woman-under-the-influence-1974-gena-rowlands-dinner-table.jpg","thumb":"https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/responsive/public/2022-02/a-woman-under-the-influence-1974-gena-rowlands-dinner-table.jpg/960x540-cropped/a-woman-under-the-influence-1974-gena-rowlands-dinner-table.jpg","preload":"https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/responsive/public/2022-02/a-woman-under-the-influence-1974-gena-rowlands-dinner-table.jpg/96x54-cropped/a-woman-under-the-influence-1974-gena-rowlands-dinner-table.jpg","altText":null},"name":"A Woman under the Influence","url":"/film/59ac010c-250e-5a0e-8cdf-65c3c5217634/a-woman-under-the-influence","summary":null,"fullDescription":"","quote":null,"credits":{"director":"John Cassavetes","producer":"Sam Shaw","writer":"John Cassavetes","featuring":"Peter Falk, Gena Rowlands, Fred Drape